{
  "texts": [
    "A majority of AI applications either exist in a state of partial development or are entirely nascent in their conception.",
    "Furthermore, the application of AI among the solutions to food security involves the adoption of regenerative agriculture and permaculture (McLennon et al., 2021).",
    "McLennon et al. (2021) illustrated that specialized monoculture cropping systems, though meeting immediate food and fiber requirements, exhibit adverse impacts on natural resources, particularly affecting the sustainability of production agriculture.",
    "Focusing on regenerative agriculture, permaculture, and smart technology, the study advocated a holistic approach aimed at reducing dependence on external inputs, such as agrochemicals and machinery, to restore and maintain natural systems.",
    "Authors indicated that the proposed adoption of modern regenerative agriculture and integrated permaculture is anticipated to enhance soil health, biodiversity, land and resource conservation, agricultural sustainability, and global food security."
  ]
}